WEBVTT

1
00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:48.260 
你妈妈一直没保养游泳池
Your mother hasn't been keeping up the pool.

2
00:17:48.260 --> 00:17:52.000 
- 你愿意的话，你可以修一下  - 好，我会的
- lf you wanted to, you could fix it. - Yeah, I will.

3
00:17:52.270 --> 00:17:53.870 
你知道化学清洗剂在哪里吧？
You know where the chemicals are?

4
00:17:53.880 --> 00:17:55.770 
我以前在你出门的时候做过，记得吗？
I used to do it when you were gone, remember?

5
00:17:55.770 --> 00:17:59.770 
我从来不怎么在家待着，威尔
I was never much for being at home, Will.

6
00:18:00.410 --> 00:18:02.010 
太拘束了
Too confining.

7
00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:05.280 
然而现在，被困在床上…
And this here, being stuck in bed…

8
00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:09.150 
等死是我一生中最糟糕的事
Dying is the worst thing that's ever happened to me.

9
00:18:09.790 --> 00:18:11.650 
我以为你说过你不会死
I thought you said you weren't dying.

10
00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:15.000 
我说的是 我不是这么走的
I said this isn't how I go.

11
00:18:15.620 --> 00:18:19.690 
最后这部分是最不寻常的
The last part is much more unusual.

